  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598518730102-KIJ0S90AQUNIYGTKA5R2/5a-IMG_1253-600x400.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Any chance I get to take a little trip to <a href=\"http://www.urbanicpaper.com/\">Urbanic</a>, I do a happy dance. This place is a feast for creative gurus and anyone who appreciates good design on a greeting card. Wanna dress up your gift with some cute paper and ribbon? This is the place to go. Wanna have them customize your stationery? Done! I spy a bit of Amy Tangerine product on their shelf! </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"5b-IMG_1242.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598518756280-S7UYBCFE5QO1PFIM614U/5b-IMG_1242.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"5c-IMG_1245.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598518756860-COWSEWYPOWAMQ0HCDT57/5c-IMG_1245.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5d-IMG_1246.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598518758623-W85SY8LYEJ9Q6WZJAOXH/5d-IMG_1246.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5e-IMG_1251.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598518759926-JCJ89HA6IU3FNNH33VYR/5e-IMG_1251.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5f-IMG_1252.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598518790628-XKPWV4BJU9OGKWD9CHSZ/5f-IMG_1252.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5g-IMG_1262.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598518790319-ATLLXHIUOD9BETWN3UHO/5g-IMG_1262.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Jack still likes hanging out and going on adventures in <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00BJCFNKU/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B00BJCFNKU&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=wwwamytangeri-20&amp;linkId=CRPHBMMOLNJBZ6AC\">the Ergo</a>. Lucky us - we bumped into the lovely <a href=\"http://www.smittenstudioonline.com/\">Sarah of smitten studio!</a></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"5h-IMG_1264.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598518873361-UZCGJTB7GLRQLV29Q1K1/5h-IMG_1264.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5i-IMG_1267.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598518872913-GFM92Y465GUG4U52HZHV/5i-IMG_1267.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5j-IMG_1269.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598518875823-PXRLMI9TRULUBVIWKCLL/5j-IMG_1269.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5k-IMG_1281.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598518876086-WOXGTLS67FO2OR4NH2SK/5k-IMG_1281.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>And the goodies that made it home with me. I wish I could bring home the entire store! Ahhh, self restraint! Photos by <a href=\"http://jacshootblog.com/\">Jamie Waters</a></p>"
}